::DrillBit::

He heard Deemos's message.
"Oh, god..."

::Hot Rod::

He slept. All he thought about was Prime. He woke up, deciding to go get
the Maximal Matrix, to use on Prime. Suddenly a surge of evil came over
him. He walked out, and saw Feline.
"Hello.....," he said, in a rough, evil voice.
